quotes.quote: The way to get started is to quit talking and begin doing.
The only way to do great work is to love what you do.
Imagination is more important than knowledge. For knowledge is limited, whereas imagination embraces the entire world, stimulating progress, giving birth to evolution.
The present is theirs; the future, for which I really work, is mine.
To be or not to be, that is the question.
Не важно с какой скоростью ты двигаешься, братишка, главное не останавливайся ежжи, пока остановка не стала последней ежжи
